        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "A New Era of Golf Fashion",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Golf has never been just about the game—it's a statement, a lifestyle, an attitude. The <strong>S&T TRENDYGOLF x G/FORE Highlight Capsule</strong> combines high-performance function with an urban-inspired edge. For those who refuse to conform to the expected, this capsule is designed to disrupt the fairways with an effortless fusion of sophistication and modern rebellion.</p><p>This exclusive drop reinvents on-course style with <strong>sleek black-on-black tones, amplified by striking pink embroidery</strong> that adds a bold contrast to every piece. It's a collection that speaks to those who demand more from their golf wardrobe—athleticism, elegance, and a fearless attitude. </p>"
          }
        }
      },
