            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The <strong>S&T TG x Highlight Capsule</strong> is crafted for golfers who want their style to be as sharp as their swing. This collection features <strong>premium materials, innovative fabrics, and contemporary fits</strong>, this collection isn't just about looking good and performing at your best. Each piece is a testament to G/FORE's signature luxury craftsmanship, fused with TRENDYGOLF's forward-thinking approach to golf fashion.</p>"
          }
        }
