    "text_3": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "The Collection:",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<ul><li><strong>S&T TG X Highlight Stretch Twill Quick Turn Hat (Onyx - SS25)<br/></strong>A lightweight essential with sleek pink detailing, perfect for keeping the sun at bay while making a statement.</li><li><strong>S&T TG X Highlight Essential 3.0 Tech Pique Polo (Onyx - SS25)<br/></strong>An elevated take on the classic polo, designed with moisture-wicking technology and stretch for full-swing mobility.</li><li><strong>S&T TG X Highlight The Stinger Hybrid Stretch Gilet (Onyx - SS25)<br/></strong>Layer up in effortless style—this hybrid gilet delivers warmth without the bulk, making it an essential transitional piece.</li><li><strong>S&T TG X Highlight Brushed Back Tech Quarter Zip Mid Layer (Onyx - SS25)<br/></strong>A sleek quarter-zip that balances warmth and breathability, engineered for both performance and off-course wearability.</li><li><strong>S&T TG X Highlight The Maverick Hybrid Stretch Jacket (Onyx - SS25)<br/></strong>A game-changer in layering, this hybrid jacket is crafted for superior comfort, movement, and technical sophistication.</li><li><strong>S&T TG X Highlight Brushed Back Tech Terry Hoodie (Onyx - SS25) </strong>A bold yet refined hoodie that effortlessly blends street style with golf-ready performance. Designed for versatility, from the driving range to post-round drinks.</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
