    "text_4": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Why This Drop Stands Out",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Golf apparel has seen its share of evolution, but the <strong>S&T TRENDYGOLF x G/FORE Highlight Capsule</strong> is on a different level. This is <strong>not</strong> just another seasonal collection—it's a <strong>statement of intent.</strong> The <strong>sleek aesthetic, performance-first construction and fashion-forward detailing</strong> create a lineup that doesn't just push boundaries; it eliminates them entirely.</p><p>The use of <strong>high-performance stretch fabrics, technical layering, and ultra-premium finishing touches</strong> ensure that each piece delivers in both function and form. And with <strong>limited availability</strong>, this is not a collection that will sit around—once it's gone, it's gone.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
