    "text_5": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Own The Course, Own The Moment",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The <strong>G/FORE Skull & Tees x TRENDYGOLF Highlight Capsule</strong> is not just about clothing; it's about defining a new standard in golf fashion. Whether you're <strong>on the course, in the clubhouse, or hitting the city after a round</strong>, this exclusive drop ensures you'll turn heads for all the right reasons.</p><p>For those who don't just play golf but live it, the <strong>S&T TG x Highlight Capsule</strong> is your next essential move.</p><p>Explore the full collection now at <a href=\"https://trendygolf.com/collections/st-tg-x-highlight-capsule-mens?_pos=1&_psq=TG+x&_ss=e&_v=1.0&filter.v.availability=1\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">TRENDYGOLF</span></a>.<br/><br/>Peter Millar/G/FORE shot at the Alfred Dunhill Links Championship</p>"
          }
        }
